summary: A restyling of Mjoll the Lioness based on Yaksha Race and ApachiiHair mods.
descriptionHtml:
My absolute first mod created with Skyrim NPC Editor.
It\'s a restyling of Mjoll the Lioness based on Yaksha Race and ApachiiHair mods.

[b]Name:[/b] Sapphire
[b]Equipment:[/b] Daedric Shield, Daedric Bow, Daedric Arrows (x50), Daedric Warhammer, some Golds and default items.
[b]Clothes:[/b] She is nude and wears only what she has in her inventory so you can give her your preferite clothes.

Enjoy :)
author: RoxasShadow
